data.description: Welcome home to the community of Sunrise Villas! This Fresh paint 3 bedroom 2 bath townhome has it all! Attached 2 car garage. an atrium, all one level, patio in the back. New: AC '13. Water Heater '13. Bathroom showers '18. Roofing '04 & '10. Updated lighting. The community has is gated and has a pool and spa for those hot Summer Vegas days!! .
